    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >QQ群：173872386</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一款 <strong>3D 武侠动作 Roguelite + 刷宝游戏</strong>。 <br>在每一次冒险中，你都需要做出抉择：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >心法的取舍，技能的搭配，还有武器的选择。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中提供多种可深度组合的武学方向： <br>火攻、冰冻、攻速、技能爆发等流派皆可自由构筑。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >刷宝 × 肉鸽的全新武侠体验</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在传统 Roguelite 玩法基础上，本作加入了<strong>刷宝掉落与局外配装</strong>机制。 <br>你可以在战斗中获得随机掉落的武器与装备，将其带出关卡，在局外进行整理、打造与搭配，再以全新的配置迎接下一次冒险。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4310740/extras/9ee3f48b26c9237153ba67f57ecc2dbe.poster.avif?t=1770010291\" width=1170 height=728 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4310740/extras/9ee3f48b26c9237153ba67f57ecc2dbe.webm?t=1770010291\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4310740/extras/9ee3f48b26c9237153ba67f57ecc2dbe.mp4?t=1770010291\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >江湖不仁，剑道将绝。 <br>门派凋零，秘卷失散，血火之后，只余残响。 <br>一场覆灭武林的事故，将整个江湖推向崩坏的边缘。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >传承未断，但只剩最后一线生机。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4310740/extras/e25e186a44a4fa57fbafaca0fb8461c2.poster.avif?t=1770010291\" width=1170 height=728 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4310740/extras/e25e186a44a4fa57fbafaca0fb8461c2.webm?t=1770010291\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4310740/extras/e25e186a44a4fa57fbafaca0fb8461c2.mp4?t=1770010291\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >画剑为刃，重铸江湖</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >那一夜之后，诸多武林门派惨遭重创，高手陨落，绝学湮灭，曾经的江湖秩序不复存在。 <br>你，作为<strong>剑宗的弟子</strong>，在乱世之中临危受命，被送往剑宗最后的据点——<strong>画剑坊</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >画剑坊并非凡俗铸剑之地。 <br>这里的画剑师，以真气入画，从纸上唤出剑的形与魂。 <br>画中之剑，化虚为实，或燃火、或凝冰、或蕴含上古异能，被称为——<strong>画中剑</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >而你，将带着这些剑，踏入破碎的武林，调查事故的真相，寻回失落的武学秘籍，为濒死的江湖争回最后的未来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4310740/extras/012a8ca6afa94f5407f9287b8c27f3fa.poster.avif?t=1770010291\" width=1170 height=728 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4310740/extras/012a8ca6afa94f5407f9287b8c27f3fa.webm?t=1770010291\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4310740/extras/012a8ca6afa94f5407f9287b8c27f3fa.mp4?t=1770010291\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2>",
